http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/karnataka/A-hoarding-that-embarrassed-Congress-workers/article13987600.ece

The Congress workers and supporters had put up hundreds of hoardings here to welcome Chief Minister Siddaramaiah and his cabinet colleagues, who had come to participate in a function on Thursday. One such hoarding, however, caught the attention of all people.The hoarding suggested that H.D. Deve Gowda, the former Prime Minister and MP from Hassan, as the Chief Minister, in the place of Siddaramaiah.It had been placed by the residents of Sankenahalli, Doddapura and Boovanahalli villages. The mistake in the hoarding embarrassed many Congress workers.